{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/pass-plus.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/pass-plus","title":"Pass Plus","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"1649","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"","overview":"Pass Plus is a practical course to improve your driving skills - once completed you may be able to get a car insurance discount","video_summary":"","video_url":"","parts":[{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/pass-plus/overview","slug":"overview","order":1,"title":"Overview","body":"<p>Pass Plus is a practical training course that takes at least 6 hours and is for drivers to improve their skills and drive more safely.</p>\n\n<p>It can be taken at any time although it should be most useful to new drivers in the year after passing their test.</p>\n\n<p>You’ll need a Pass Plus registered approved driving instructor (<abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr>) to teach you.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>It may help you get a car insurance discount if you successfully complete the course .</p>\n</div>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/pass-plus/booking-pass-plus","slug":"booking-pass-plus","order":2,"title":"Booking Pass Plus","body":"\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You need to book Pass Plus with a Pass Plus registered approved driving instructor (<abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr>).</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You can contact the Driving Standards Agency (<abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>) to check if an instructor is registered with Pass Plus. You’ll need their name and <abbr title=\"Approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> number.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> Pass Plus team</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#112;&#097;&#115;&#115;&#112;&#108;&#117;&#115;&#064;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#046;&#103;&#115;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#112;&#097;&#115;&#115;&#112;&#108;&#117;&#115;&#064;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#046;&#103;&#115;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n0115 936 6504<br />\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 4pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Fees</h2>\n\n<p>Pass Plus fees depend on where you live, the instructor or driving school and how long your training takes.</p>\n\n<p>Some <a href=\"/pass-plus/local-councils-offering-discounts\" title=\"Local councils offering Pass Plus discounts\">local councils can offer discounts</a> off the full Pass Plus training costs. </p>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/pass-plus/local-councils-offering-discounts","slug":"local-councils-offering-discounts","order":3,"title":"Local councils offering discounts","body":"<p>Some local councils can offer discounts off the full Pass Plus training costs</p>\n\n<p>Contact your borough, town, city or county council if they are listed to see if they can help you with the cost of your training.</p>\n\n<h2>East Midlands</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Derby City Council</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#100;&#101;&#114;&#098;&#121;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#100;&#101;&#114;&#098;&#121;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n01332 641 778</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Lincolnshire County Council</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#115;&#116;&#097;&#121;&#105;&#110;&#103;&#097;&#108;&#105;&#118;&#101;&#064;&#108;&#105;&#110;&#099;&#111;&#108;&#110;&#115;&#104;&#105;&#114;&#101;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#115;&#116;&#097;&#121;&#105;&#110;&#103;&#097;&#108;&#105;&#118;&#101;&#064;&#108;&#105;&#110;&#099;&#111;&#108;&#110;&#115;&#104;&#105;&#114;&#101;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n01522 805 800</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Rutland County Council</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#101;&#110;&#113;&#117;&#105;&#114;&#105;&#101;&#115;&#064;&#114;&#117;&#116;&#108;&#097;&#110;&#100;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#101;&#110;&#113;&#117;&#105;&#114;&#105;&#101;&#115;&#064;&#114;&#117;&#116;&#108;&#097;&#110;&#100;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n01572 722 577</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>North West</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Cheshire West and Chester Council</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#099;&#104;&#101;&#115;&#104;&#105;&#114;&#101;&#119;&#101;&#115;&#116;&#097;&#110;&#100;&#099;&#104;&#101;&#115;&#116;&#101;&#114;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#099;&#104;&#101;&#115;&#104;&#105;&#114;&#101;&#119;&#101;&#115;&#116;&#097;&#110;&#100;&#099;&#104;&#101;&#115;&#116;&#101;&#114;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Cumbria</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.crsp.co.uk\" title=\"www.crsp.co.uk\" rel=\"external\">www.crsp.co.uk</a><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#099;&#104;&#114;&#105;&#115;&#046;&#098;&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#098;&#101;&#110;&#116;&#064;&#099;&#117;&#109;&#098;&#114;&#105;&#097;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#099;&#104;&#114;&#105;&#115;&#046;&#098;&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#098;&#101;&#110;&#116;&#064;&#099;&#117;&#109;&#098;&#114;&#105;&#097;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n01228 221751</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Wirral Council</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wirral.gov.uk/roadsafety\" title=\"www.wirral.gov.uk/roadsafety\" rel=\"external\">www.wirral.gov.uk/roadsafety</a><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#119;&#105;&#114;&#114;&#097;&#108;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#119;&#105;&#114;&#114;&#097;&#108;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>South East</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Hampshire County Council</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#046;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#104;&#097;&#110;&#116;&#115;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#046;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#104;&#097;&#110;&#116;&#115;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hants.gov.uk/roadsafety\" title=\"www.hants.gov.uk/roadsafety\" rel=\"external\">www.hants.gov.uk/roadsafety</a><br />\n01962 846 100</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Kent County Council</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#112;&#097;&#115;&#115;&#046;&#112;&#108;&#117;&#115;&#064;&#107;&#101;&#110;&#116;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#112;&#097;&#115;&#115;&#046;&#112;&#108;&#117;&#115;&#064;&#107;&#101;&#110;&#116;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>West Midlands</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Staffordshire County Council</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#115;&#116;&#097;&#102;&#102;&#111;&#114;&#100;&#115;&#104;&#105;&#114;&#101;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#115;&#116;&#097;&#102;&#102;&#111;&#114;&#100;&#115;&#104;&#105;&#114;&#101;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n0300 111 8012</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Telford and Wrekin Council</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#116;&#101;&#108;&#102;&#111;&#114;&#100;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#116;&#101;&#108;&#102;&#111;&#114;&#100;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Scotland</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Argyll and Bute Council</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#106;&#117;&#110;&#101;&#046;&#103;&#114;&#097;&#104;&#097;&#109;&#064;&#097;&#114;&#103;&#121;&#108;&#108;&#045;&#098;&#117;&#116;&#101;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#106;&#117;&#110;&#101;&#046;&#103;&#114;&#097;&#104;&#097;&#109;&#064;&#097;&#114;&#103;&#121;&#108;&#108;&#045;&#098;&#117;&#116;&#101;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n01546 604 182</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Fife Council</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#115;&#117;&#112;&#112;&#111;&#114;&#116;&#117;&#110;&#105;&#116;&#064;&#102;&#105;&#102;&#101;&#046;&#112;&#110;&#110;&#046;&#112;&#111;&#108;&#105;&#099;&#101;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#115;&#117;&#112;&#112;&#111;&#114;&#116;&#117;&#110;&#105;&#116;&#064;&#102;&#105;&#102;&#101;&#046;&#112;&#110;&#110;&#046;&#112;&#111;&#108;&#105;&#099;&#101;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n01383 318 604</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Highland Council</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#046;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#104;&#105;&#103;&#104;&#108;&#097;&#110;&#100;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#114;&#111;&#097;&#100;&#046;&#115;&#097;&#102;&#101;&#116;&#121;&#064;&#104;&#105;&#103;&#104;&#108;&#097;&#110;&#100;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n01463 702 690</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Wales</h2>\n\n<p>All local councils in Wales offer discounted Pass Plus courses. Visit the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.dragondriver.com/ppcindex.htm\" title=\"Pass Plus Cymru\">Pass Plus Cymru</a> website for more information.</p>\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/pass-plus/how-pass-plus-training-works","slug":"how-pass-plus-training-works","order":4,"title":"How Pass Plus training works","body":"<p>Pass Plus training takes at least 6 hours. It has 6 modules, covering driving:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>in town</li>\n  <li>in all weathers</li>\n  <li>on rural roads</li>\n  <li>at night</li>\n  <li>on dual carriageways</li>\n  <li>on motorways</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>All modules should be practical sessions, although local conditions may mean some are theory based. You’ll normally spend at least 5.5 hours driving.</p>\n\n<p>You won’t take a test but you’ll be assessed throughout the course. To pass you&rsquo;ll have to reach the required standard in all modules.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You’ll be sent a Pass Plus certificate after you’ve successfully finished your training. You’ll need this when applying for a car insurance discount.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>For more information about Pass Plus contact the Driving Standards Agency (<abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>) Pass Plus team</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> Pass Plus team</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#112;&#097;&#115;&#115;&#112;&#108;&#117;&#115;&#064;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#046;&#103;&#115;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#112;&#097;&#115;&#115;&#112;&#108;&#117;&#115;&#064;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#046;&#103;&#115;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n0115 936 6504<br />\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 4pm</p>\n</div>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/pass-plus/car-insurance-discounts","slug":"car-insurance-discounts","order":5,"title":"Car insurance discounts","body":"<p>Once you’ve completed Pass Plus you may be able to get a car insurance discount. You’ll need your Pass Plus certificate.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>Check with insurers that you can still get a discount if you passed your practical driving test more than a year ago.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>The amount of discount depends on the insurance company. Not all insurers offer Pass Plus discounts.</p>\n\n<p>You might be able to put the discount on hold for up to 2 years if you don’t have a car at the moment - check with the insurance company first.</p>\n"}]},"updated_at":"2012-10-14T16:50:55+00:00","tags":[{"title":"Driving tests and learning to drive","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/driving%2Flearning-to-drive.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes booking a test, changing and cancelling tests, rules and fees","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=driving%2Flearning-to-drive","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving/learning-to-drive"},"parent":{"title":"Driving, transport and travel","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/driving.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Book your driving test or get a tax disc online, find out the legal requirements for buying, owning, importing or scrapping a car or motorcycle, and read about your rights and responsibilities as a driver.","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=driving","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving"},"parent":null}},{"title":"MOT and vehicle insurance","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/driving%2Fmot-insurance.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes getting an MOT, MOT fees and vehicle insurance","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=driving%2Fmot-insurance","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving/mot-insurance"},"parent":{"title":"Driving, transport and travel","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/driving.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Book your driving test or get a tax disc online, find out the legal requirements for buying, owning, importing or scrapping a car or motorcycle, and read about your rights and responsibilities as a driver.","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=driving","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving"},"parent":null}},{"title":"Directgov","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/directgov.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=directgov","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/directgov"},"parent":null}],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/enhanced-rider-scheme.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/enhanced-rider-scheme","title":"Enhanced rider scheme","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"1659","business_proposition":false},"updated_at":"2012-10-13T19:26:31+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/vehicle-insurance.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/vehicle-insurance","title":"Vehicle insurance","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"33","business_proposition":false},"updated_at":"2012-10-13T19:29:50+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/pass-plus-approved-driving-instructor-services.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/pass-plus-approved-driving-instructor-services","title":"Pass Plus approved driving instructor (ADI) services","format":"transaction","details":{"need_id":"B182","business_proposition":true},"updated_at":"2012-10-14T16:47:29+00:00"}]}